{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"0acc75ee-d2e3-4e32-9754-a14ec199c7f5","content":"Here's what you need:\n\n### Environment Variables\n\nAdd these to your container spec:\n\n```yaml\nenv:\n  # Enable automatic crash dump generation\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump\n    value: \"1\"\n  # Dump type: 1=Mini, 2=Heap, 3=Triage, 4=Full\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType\n    value: \"4\"\n  # Path to createdump tool (required for NativeAOT)\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath\n    value: \"/opt/tools/createdump\"\n  # Dump output path (%d = PID, %t = timestamp)\n  - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName\n    value: \"/tmp/dumps/coredump.%d.%t\"\n```\n\n### Pod Spec Changes\n\n```yaml\nspec:\n  containers:\n    - name: your-app\n      # ... existing config ...\n      env:\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump\n          value: \"1\"\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType\n          value: \"4\"\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath\n          value: \"/opt/tools/createdump\"\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName\n          value: \"/tmp/dumps/coredump.%d.%t\"\n      securityContext:\n        capabilities:\n          add:\n            - SYS_PTRACE       # required for createdump to attach\n      volumeMounts:\n        - name: dump-volume\n          mountPath: /tmp/dumps\n  volumes:\n    - name: dump-volume\n      emptyDir:\n        sizeLimit: 2Gi        # adjust based on expected dump size\n```\n\n### Key points\n\n- **`SYS_PTRACE`** capability is mandatory — `createdump` uses `ptrace` to read process memory.\n- **`DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath`** is required for NativeAOT since the runtime doesn't bundle `createdump`.\n- Use **type `4` (Full)** for complete dumps; use `2` (Heap) if size is a concern.\n- Mount a volume at the dump path so dumps survive container restarts and can be retrieved (e.g., via `kubectl cp` or a sidecar that ships them to blob storage).","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"550f2eab-c873-4143-8a91-6270bec3e966","outputTokens":594,"requestId":"6015:BAB4E:DB77A5:FEEBF8:69EACACB"},"id":"c14a122d-6363-4451-b3fd-3fff1d2f4eac","timestamp":"2026-04-24T01:43:54.851Z","parentId":"18d02547-fc9c-4b5a-939b-309eb9699c8e"}
